instance->instance[friends]
instance->static[enemy]
static->staic[friend]
static->instance[not good combination]

instance->it is part of object
static->it is part of class 

can i access data member or variable from static to instance?
NO

The static field Test1.b should be accessed in a static way


public class Test3 {


	static int b=10;//static variable
	
	//instance 
	static void display() {
		System.out.println("Static variable b "+ b);
	}
	public static void main(String[] args) {
		//How to acess static method?->using class name 
		Test3.display();

	}

}









public class Test1 {
	
	int a=10;//instance
	static int b=20;//static variable

	public static void main(String[] args) {
		Test1 t=new Test1();//instace
		System.out.println(t.a);//10
		System.out.println(Test1.b);//static using class
		System.out.println(t.b);

	}

}



public class Test {
	
	//instance variable
	int num1=100;
	int num2=150;
	
	//static method->class level method 
	static void m1() {
		System.out.println(num1);
		System.out.println(num2);

	}
	
	//static method->class level method 
	static void m2() {
		System.out.println(num1);
		System.out.println(num2);
	}

	public static void main(String[] args) {
		Test t=new Test();//create an object
		t.m1();//static method 
		t.m2();//static method

	}

}


Variable:
1.static variable
2.instance variable
3.local variable





public class Test3 {
	
	//static variable
	static int num1=20;
	
	//static method 
	static void display() {
		//local variable
		int localdata=30;//local variable 
		System.out.println("Static variable num1 :"+ num1);//20
		System.out.println("Local variable :"+localdata);//30
	}

	public static void main(String[] args) {
		display();
	}

}



use of constructor
//parent class 
class Parent{
	//constructor
	Parent(){
		System.out.println("This is parent class constructor.");
	}
}


//inheritance 
class Child extends Parent{
	//constructor
	Child(){
		super();
		System.out.println("This is child class constructor");
	}
}


public class Main {

	public static void main(String[] args) {
		
		//create child class object 
//		Child childobj=new Child();

		//create paren object
		Parent parentobj=new Parent();
		
	}

}



